data.text:
Our roots trace back to the 1940’s, making us one of the most well-established brokerages in Alberta. Our customer-focused approach, combined with our experience, helps our customers feel more confident about the future.

Whether you’re a growing family looking for a bigger home or an entrepreneur investing in new equipment, your insurance broker will take the time to learn your unique situation. Learn more about our personal approach.

Direct-Line Insurance has several branches across Alberta. We offer personal service built on one-on-one relationships. Each Insurance Broker takes care of specific clients. We provide guidance and support for each client, helping them choose the coverage and options that will match their particular need. Additionally, both the Millet and Warburg branches offer AB Registries Services and ATB Banking Services. We’re here to help you with all of your financial needs. Get started by finding a branch near you.
